xal.smf.impl

Class Electromagnet

  • java.lang.Object
    • xal.smf.AcceleratorNode
      • xal.smf.impl.Magnet
        • xal.smf.impl.Electromagnet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ElementType, MagnetType, DataListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Dipole, Quadrupole, Sextupole, Solenoid

    public abstract class Electromagnet
extends Magnet
    Electromagnet is the base class representation of an electromagnet.

        public int getCycleState()
